25.000Z","msg":"如果去返之前已經去過嘅地方，就唔plan都無問題"},{"pid":"6a2eb7ecf4fbe0ee5655c801b812815eb6b7ef7c","tid":2022910,"uid":34771,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"2c778f1f675fe6e3df328d2b2451f5e70098379b","tid":2022910,"uid":22974,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:27:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"變左日日Google 仲攰過預早plan定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9e5634cdbd26afdd006262d56ae9a7ee093163","tid":2022910,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:13:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da0eb845917f6630e1db179a167d9c59be4dfabd","tid":2022910,"uid":213945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:33:23.000Z","msg":"英國exchange 個時無咩朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過第一次歐洲solo trip (個次上個月前plan)之後 上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即興會今日book聽日/ 後日 去其他城市 <br />\n(Edinburgh, London, Belfast) 呢幾次都係每個城市stay 三日兩夜咁 <br />\n其實有手機上到網 , 有信用卡就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慳錢backpack hostel就帶毛巾, 拖鞋, travel kit<br />\n<br />\n不過如果係香港出發 就唔會去咁遠,, <br />\n返到黎就只係即興去過兩次 <br />\n一個星期台灣 一個星期台灣"},{"pid":"76368b99d3f5d7493c54d24cec2a613fdb64f6e6","tid":2022910,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:40:10.000Z","msg":"試過禮拜尾去京都，去到日日10點零11點起身食野先諗嗰日去邊，反正無乜所謂，志在hea幾日就算"},{"pid":"44744ac86aff2ae0b96352e46cff113f00880314","tid":2022910,"uid":96032,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"da0eb845917f6630e1db179a167d9c59be4dfabd","tid":2022910,"uid":213945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:33:23.000Z","msg":"英國exchange 個時無咩朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過第一次歐洲solo trip (個次上個月前plan)之後 上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即興會今日book聽日/ 後日 去其他城市 <br />\n(Edinburgh, London, Belfast) 呢幾次都係每個城市stay 三日兩夜咁 <br />\n其實有手機上到網 , 有信用卡就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慳錢backpack hostel就帶毛巾, 拖鞋, travel kit<br />\n<br />\n不過如果係香港出發 就唔會去咁遠,, <br />\n返到黎就只係即興去過兩次 <br />\n一個星期台灣 一個星期台灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:58:46.000Z","msg":"一樣exchange冇朋友，一個人自己去旅行<br />\n今日book酒店機票，聽日或者後日飛<br />\n落機後先上網睇點出市區去酒店<br />\ncheck in咗先喺房上trip advisor plan一陣去邊，夜晚返嚟再plan第二日行程<br />\n因為冇做過功課，唔知應該玩幾多日<br />\n試過book 4日，去到發覺兩日鬆啲就冇嘢睇，鳩下鳩下鳩咗兩日<br />\n又試過book 3日，發覺唔夠時間，最後一日十一點鐘機，玩到夜晚十點幾先到機場，晚飯都冇食<br />\n真心刺激，好enjoy一落機乜都唔知，人生路不熟果種感覺<br />\n之後去旅行應該都唔會plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4956eacb2cf723bf1ea590771a266fd7f8109348","tid":2022910,"uid":75359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T18:59:40.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔plan，睇下人地遊記買張機票就去得，上年去到以色列因為無預先訂回程機票同酒店比人的左入房傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我英文仲要麻麻土木<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />解釋完先放行"},{"pid":"36bb3dcc51490d2850e198970cb2828f314ae916","tid":2022910,"uid":312205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T19:01:53.000Z","msg":"出發前個幾禮拜<br />\n見到飛沖繩宮古島一千出頭<br />\n諗都冇諗就買咗<br />\n喺機場先知交通好唔方便<br />\n自己又冇車牌<br />\n去到行下海灘<br />\n行下藥房<br />\n喺民宿識咗幾個日本人<br />\n搭順風車一齊玩食個飯<br />\n三日兩夜快閃<br />\n幾正"},{"pid":"0e2920d7a29162b6a252d9bdf7a2b7f1720155a6","tid":2022910,"uid":84472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T20:56:59.000Z","msg":"最鐘意咩都唔plan 到時先算 <br />\n坐都唔坐 鳩行<br />\n試過喺Ams行咗3日"},{"pid":"28d2c15f01b4b72c2ae6761cf7ced88068208040","tid":2022910,"uid":10845,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T21:09:14.000Z","msg":"即興就填visa 4日後驗身，7日批左就出發澳洲working holiday <br />\n個陣十九歲去到冇book任何酒店。<br />\n坐左係機場四個鐘上背包客棧第一時間識個朋友<br />\n坐火車去搵佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同依家都冇後悔當日衝動去working holiday <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908fa5135633ff8d1b5d285f46dc3122360c7536","tid":2022910,"uid":56230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:40:30.000Z","msg":"幾年前訓醒想去西藏就坐車去紅磡買2個星期後火車飛<br />\n跟住返屋企訂埋青旅同回程機票<br />\n抄低青旅個地址同幾個景區名就乜都無理<br />\n但早幾年係西藏遇到班大陸人都好熱情 係青旅join埋一齊玩 都無乜大問題"},{"pid":"04fb7f7da3d61945d037b3bb1d87000e5eeaabb0","tid":2022910,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"去親泰國都冇plan<br />\n頹廢每日訓醒食完早餐再訓 訓到4-5點就出去搵野食 再行夜市商場<br />\n試過去2星期咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edb115d5d8bdda25138c99897fad6c44956640f","tid":2022910,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"點為之即興先。<br />\n支那就試過<br />\n遠嘅地方。唔好話plan唔plan行程。你冇資料搜集。你去到會miss咗好多嘢<br />\n點都會係咁二...睇下"},{"pid":"f0134bd993af348772dbf8c5a8d26d7474e7b468","tid":2022910,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T04:25:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">光復香港，要你幫手！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【丫叉郵包案】<span style=\"color: orange;\">眾籌民事訴訟控告警方</span></strong><br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cMLSEJ&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=3959edb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【612基金】<span style=\"color: orange;\">大量手足上庭，基金只剩幾三千萬！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://612fund.hk/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fdonate&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2